  12 Nov 2004; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org> flobopuyo-0.20.ebuild:
  Added ~amd64 KEYWORDS and closing bug #69656.

  05 Nov 2004; Joseph Jezak <josejx@gentoo.org> flobopuyo-0.20.ebuild:
